{
  "texts": [
    "In other words, we create a lookup table connecting values of u train to the best α in α train.",
    "For new pixels, α is determined by the closest norm in the lookup table.",
    "Spot calling.",
    "To call spots, Gaussian smoothing is applied to individual OLS maps, followed by peak_local_max filter (scikit-image 0.19.3 91) which returns a binary image with 1's at the local maxima of the smoothed OLS maps.",
    "These peaks are then used as markers for watershed segmentation."
  ]
}